<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no, email=no, date=no, address=no">
    <title>自选</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/api.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/aui.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/sl_common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/swiper.min.css">
    <style>
         html,
        body {
            
            background-color: #010646;
            height: 100%;
        }
        body {
            padding-top: 5px;
        }
           /* 新闻部分 */
    .news_item {
        position: relative;
        padding: 10px;
        height: 100px;
        background-color: #111453;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        box-sizing: content-box;
    }
    .news_item_l {
        position: absolute;
        left: 10;
        height: 100%;
        width: 50%;
    }
    .news_item_r {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 100%;
        width: 40%;
    }
    .news_item_r img {
        height: 100%;
        width: 100%;
    }
    .news_item_l_t {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        font-size: 14px;
    }
    .news_item_l_b {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 12px;
        width: 100%;
    }
    .news_item_l_b .stock_name {
        float: left;
    }
    .news_item_l_b .stock_pblish_time {
        float: right;
    }

    </style>
</head>

<body>
        <section class="news_template">
                <div class="news_item">
                    <div class="news_item_l">
                        <div class="news_item_l_t">巨峰投顾：逆袭下A股能否走出自己的个性？</div>
                        <div class="news_item_l_b">
                            <div class="stock_name">巨峰投顾</div>
                            <div class="stock_pblish_time">16:41</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="news_item_r">
                        <img src="../image/stock_news_img.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="news_item">
                    <div class="news_item_l">
                        <div class="news_item_l_t">8月15日异动股点评：5G老妖股卷土重来 盘点四牛与四熊</div>
                        <div class="news_item_l_b">
                            <div class="stock_name">山东神光</div>
                            <div class="stock_pblish_time">16:41</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="news_item_r">
                        <img src="../image/stock_news_img.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="news_item">
                    <div class="news_item_l">
                        <div class="news_item_l_t">美股暴跌800点：衰退魔咒来了 特朗普急呼太疯狂！ 欧洲也出黑田野 全球市场惊魂未定</div>
                        <div class="news_item_l_b">
                            <div class="stock_name">山东神光</div>
                            <div class="stock_pblish_time">16:41</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="news_item_r">
                        <img src="../image/stock_news_img.png" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
</body>

</html>